& [CurrentAttentionRuntimeRegistryState] is the live semantic registry for active attention
  + [registry_status] is active
  + [registry_scope] is six-family LM Studio worker readiness synthesis
  + [active_root_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_readiness_synthesis
  + [active_frame_count] is 1
  + [suspended_frame_count] is 0
  + [closed_frame_count] is 7
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [registry_outside] is hidden activations, exact transformer attention, model weights, worker mutation authority, broad task competence, copy-exact overclaim, and unrelated Pinky worktree changes

  = must: update this state when focus materially changes
  = must: preserve return anchors before closing or suspending frames
  = must: keep the registry semantic and visible, not native-runtime or hidden-state based
  = should: stay compact enough for context-compression re-entry

& [AttentionFrame_2026_06_24_LMStudioReadinessSynthesis] is the active semantic stack frame for synthesizing six-family worker readiness
  + [frame_id] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_readiness_synthesis
  + [frame_state] is active
  + [parent_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_second_corpus_queue
  + [child_frame_set] is functional_lmstudio_lane, one_minute_heartbeat, operating_loop_tick_013, six_family_corpus, readiness_profile, outside_boundary, commit_receipt
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [frame_trace] is lmstudio_diverse_corpus_launch_queue_001.sop, lmstudio_diverse_corpus_launch_queue_002.sop, integration_disposition_review_015.sop, 2026-06-24_operating_loop_tick_013.sop, and CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [focus_register] is compile six-family readiness synthesis
  + [question_register] is how to name the worker lane capability without broad competence, project-root authority, mutation authority, or direct trust overclaim
  + [delineation_register] is inside six family signals, retry ladders, validator latches, accepted outputs, and synthesis outside
  + [periphery_register] is broad competence outside, project-root authority outside, worker mutation outside, direct trust outside, and unrelated dirty files outside
  + [operation_register] is synthesize_evidence, classify_readiness, preserve_outside, define_next_gate, emit_next_tick
  + [evidence_register] is six family pass count, completed first queue, completed second queue, and operating_loop_tick_013
  + [wisdom_register] is complete corpus evidence can improve confidence for the narrow scratch-isolated worker lane
  + [caution_register] is six family passes still do not prove broad LM Studio competence, project-root safety, mutation authority, or autonomous task execution
  + [balance_register] is stable because no worker launch is needed for the synthesis step
  + [integration_register] is pending synthesis, commit, push, and next-gate selection
  + [frame_outside] is hidden model state, worker file mutation, remote claims before push, broad local-worker readiness, and unrelated workspace changes

  = must: treat this frame as current visible attention state
  = must: return clock_state, proof_state, balance_state, drive_state, next_step, and outside to CurrentFocalPoint when this focus pass closes
  = should: open child frames only when a concrete benchmark, scoring, or worker-profile pass is needed

